Come help increase new PA's  astronomical knowledge while rediscovering the mysteries above us! Helping to deliver the course material in the astronomy class is much easier if you have an understanding of what it is all about. Come see the new activities before anyone else. This event costs $10.00 per girl, $7 per adult, lunch is included. This is a day-time program and no telescopic viewing is planned with this training.

**Program Aides who have been previously astronomy trained and have helped at 3 astronomy events in the last year may register for this session.  All adults attending this session must be registered & approved volunteers, Adult ratios are per Safety Activity Checkpoints.
